WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.501 --> 00:00:06.598
 Open MediaCoder as Administrator (Windows Vista) 

00:00:21.159 --> 00:00:25.958
 Add the video you want to convert 

00:00:36.882 --> 00:00:42.846
 For better quality see the video and audio bitrate rate and select the one closest to the conversion. 

00:00:45.662 --> 00:00:54.894
 NOTE: The higher the bitrate rate, the bigger the video size will be 

00:01:11.007 --> 00:01:14.174
 In the FPS field select "Original" 

00:01:16.518 --> 00:01:20.863
 Select the resolution according to your iPod 

00:01:25.438 --> 00:01:28.718
 In the crop option, click auto crop 

00:01:31.798 --> 00:01:37.686
 If you have caption, click subtitle and select it. 

00:01:41.982 --> 00:01:47.047
 NOTE: You can change the font, size, blur and more of your caption here 

00:01:52.327 --> 00:01:57.247
 Now choose a folder for the converted video 

00:01:57.282 --> 00:02:04.887
 NOTE: It may be the same "original" folder (which is the video you are converting) 

00:02:17.608 --> 00:02:22.735
 Press Start and start the conversion 

00:02:41.079 --> 00:02:47.311
 When you finish this message will appear, press ok. 

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:56.847
 Ready! Just skip to iTunes 

00:03:05.319 --> 00:03:11.478
 Go to the folder you chose to place the video 

00:03:18.759 --> 00:03:27.294
 Open itunes and drag the video into your library 

00:03:38.326 --> 00:03:44.294
 It's over, your video is ready for your iPhone / iPod! 

00:03:44.329 --> 00:04:08.592
